With this Framework I want to showcase and implement the following features
    - Support all famous browsers for test execution
    - Support test execution for different environments such as Testing, Staging, and Production
    - Execution environment and browser should be configured in file
    - Logging of all the steps
    - Easy to understand execution report
    - Should support common features of Web application such as Alert, IFrames, etc
    - Test data and configuration should be driven by Properties files
    - Supports CI-CD process

Tools and Technologies
    - VScode
    - Java
    - Selenium
    - Maven
    - Cucumber BDD
    - TestNG
    - Log4J2
    - Extent report
    - AShot for screenshot